$ Oracle hint: OPTIMIZER_FEATURES_ENABLE
@ optimizer_features_enable

MOS Note 2757338.1 points out that using this hint sets all optimizer related parameters to their default values.

The value of the hint itself can also be set to → https://twitter.com/ExaGridDba/status/1603783438485622787[`/*+ optimizer_features_enable(default) */`].

sa:

  Other → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/hints[hints] such as
    • `→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/optimizer/features_enable[optimizer_features_enable` and
    • `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/hints/list/opt/param`


